<p><strong>Function Description</strong>   </p>

<p>Complete the <em>canWin</em> function in the editor below.   </p>

<p><em>canWin</em> has the following parameters:   </p>

<ul>
<li><em>int leap:</em> the size of the leap   </li>
<li><em>int game[n]:</em> the array to traverse   </li>
</ul>

<p><strong>Returns</strong>   </p>

<ul>
<li><em>boolean:</em> true if the game can be won, otherwise false   </li>
